name: Lisa
description: Hello there I am a single young lady, very caring, loving, understanding, serious, open minded and very trust worthy. I like reading, singing, cooking,listening to music,watching adventure, horror and comedy movies and i also like jogging. I like to go out on a visit to the children\’s home and i like having nice and quiet times alone sometimes. I am single and searching for a man who is understanding to settle down to build our own world together full of happiness. I have no kids and wouldn’t mind having some in the nearest future.
